        i.fas.fa-envelope-square
    .content--main.grid
      .row
        .col-1-2
          h1 Vona Research Group
          p
            |Our research uses the most advanced genomics technologies to identify molecular changes in patients’
            |DNA that are associated with hereditary hearing loss. Our interests include the identification of new
            |hearing loss genes that will translate into improved molecular genetic diagnostics, as well as identifying
            |genetic changes in known genes to better understand hearing loss outcomes in patients.

